      <prop type="x-translation-ref">澤陂.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>彼澤之陂，有蒲菡萏。有美一人，碩大且儼。寤寐無為，輾轉伏枕。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>By the shores of that marsh,
There are rushes and lotus flowers.
There is that beautiful lady,
Tall and large, and majestic.
Waking or sleeping, I do nothing;
On my side, on my back, with my face on the pillow, I lie.</seg>
      </tuv>
